title: In MAGA-Led Shasta County, Election Apprehension Reigns
description: “This is not the Shasta County I know,” said Cathy Darling Allen, who has been overseeing elections in the county for 18 years.
media:credit: Mike Kai Chen for The New York Times
media:description: Cathy Darling Allen, the Shasta County clerk and registrar of voters, in her Redding office.
